scopeContent.description:
1) 'Photograph of Miss de Silva, cabinet size, No 44022-13, full length, sitting in chair, full face, dressed as a boy with leg over arm of chair and hands in pockets'. 3cm x 2cm.

2) 'Photograph of Miss de Silva, cabinet size, No 44022-14, ¾ length standing, ¾ face, as Ophelia, wearing cloak, holding spray of flowers in hands and flowers at left side of hair'. 3cm x 2cm.

3) 'Photograph of Miss de Silva, cabinet size, No 44022-15, ¾ length sitting, full face in chair, holding spray of flowers on knee and flowers in hair'. 3cm x 2cm.

4) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-1. Group of two, Mr Martin Harvey sitting resting his arms on his knees looking at Mr Aynstey across table, sitting resting his right arm on table'. 3cm x 2cm.

5) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-2. Group of two, Mr Martin Harvey sitting resting left arm on table and pointing behind him with right hand. Mr Anstey sitting opposite him resting arms on table and right hand supporting chin'. 3cm x 3cm.

6) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-3. Group of two, Mr Martin Harvey sitting with legs stretched out, resting right hand on knee and left hand on hilt of sword, looking at Miss Coleridge. She sitting the other side of table, resting right hand on it'. 3cm x 3cm.

7) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-4. Group of two, Mr Martin Harvey and Miss de Silva, both standing back view, wearing boys' clothes, both wearing hats'. 3cm x 3cm.

8) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-5. Group, Mr Martin Harvey standing at right of picture fencing with four men. A man standing on stairs at left of picture'. 3cm x 3cm.

9) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-6. Group, Mr Martin Harvey standing smoking pipe and right heel to ground, looking at man being held by two other men. A man standing at left with drawn sword, two other men standing at right'. 3cm x 3cm.

10) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-7. Group, Mr Martin Harvey sitting with head bound up and arm in sling, holding Mr Glenny (standing beside him) by the sleeve of his left arm. A man sitting at table at left writing and looking at them'. 3cm x 3cm.

11) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-8. A group, a man standing at right of picture. Mr Wright sitting at table. Mr Glenny standing by him with hand on back of chair. Mr Harvey in his shirt sleeves, being searched by a man. A man kneeling down at left examining paper'. 3cm x 3cm.

12) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-11. Group, a man lying on ground. Mr Harvey standing with right foot on bottom stair looking at him. A man standing at left holding Mr Harvey by hand looking at him. Other men grouped round'. 3cm x 3cm.

13) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-12. Group, a man with white hair standing at right, pointing with right hand. Mr Wright Senr sitting at table and Mr Glenny standing beside him. Mr Harvey standing drawing his sword and a man standing on steps at left pointing gun. Other men grouped round'. 3cm x 3cm.

14) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-14. Group Mr Anstey standing at left being held up by two men. Mr Harvey standing at right starting back pretending to be afraid, soldiers standing at back'. 3cm x 3cm.

15) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-15. Group of two, Mr Harvey standing with hat on, smoking pipe holding out paper. Mr Anstey standing profile, trying to reach paper with right hand'. 3cm x 3cm.

16) 'Photograph of Miss de Silva, cabinet size, No 44022-12, full length, kneeling on ground full face as 'Ophelia', hands folded, bunch of flowers at left side of hair'. 3cm x 3cm.

5) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-2. Group of two, Mr Martin Harvey sitting resting left arm on table and pointing behind him with right hand. Mr Anstey sitting opposite him resting arms on table and right hand supporting chin'. 3cm x 3cm.
6) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-3. Group of two, Mr Martin Harvey sitting with legs stretched out, resting right hand on knee and left hand on hilt of sword, looking at Miss Coleridge. She sitting the other side of table, resting right hand on it'. 3cm x 3cm.
7) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-4. Group of two, Mr Martin Harvey and Miss de Silva, both standing back view, wearing boys' clothes, both wearing hats'. 3cm x 3cm.
8) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-5. Group, Mr Martin Harvey standing at right of picture fencing with four men. A man standing on stairs at left of picture'. 3cm x 3cm.
9) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-6. Group, Mr Martin Harvey standing smoking pipe and right heel to ground, looking at man being held by two other men. A man standing at left with drawn sword, two other men standing at right'. 3cm x 3cm.
10) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-7. Group, Mr Martin Harvey sitting with head bound up and arm in sling, holding Mr Glenny (standing beside him) by the sleeve of his left arm. A man sitting at table at left writing and looking at them'. 3cm x 3cm.
11) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-8. A group, a man standing at right of picture. Mr Wright sitting at table. Mr Glenny standing by him with hand on back of chair. Mr Harvey in his shirt sleeves, being searched by a man. A man kneeling down at left examining paper'. 3cm x 3cm.
12) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-11. Group, a man lying on ground. Mr Harvey standing with right foot on bottom stair looking at him. A man standing at left holding Mr Harvey by hand looking at him. Other men grouped round'. 3cm x 3cm.
13) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-12. Group, a man with white hair standing at right, pointing with right hand. 14) 'Photograph of 'The Breed of the Treshams', whole plate size, No 44029-14. Group Mr Anstey standing at left being held up by two men. Mr Harvey standing at right starting back pretending to be afraid, soldiers standing at back'. 3cm x 3cm.
